snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedBytesDownload

client = AsyncSeedBytesDownload(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.service.simple()


asyncio.run(main())
